OOC: Oh swell. that shot down that post didn't it. *smirks* Looks like I'll 
have to repost then won't I. *mutters under breath*


Feline:::

She took the air-land cruser and went for the other pred base.  She hoped to 
get the DNA samples requested of her.

While hovering about 15 feet above the ground, the cruisers engines start to 
give out. "Oh no. Not good. This isn't purrrrfect timing here. You lousy 
bucket of bolts, keep going."  The craft stopped and went crashing into the 
ground.  Feline got out of the pilot's seat and got out of the cruiser. She 
kicked it with her foot and looked around. "TO THE PIT!!!!"  She transformed 
into leopard mode and went sprinting along.  She hoped that no one would 
find the cruiser untill she was well out of scanner range.  But if her luck 
was this bad to begin with, then she had no reason to think things would get 
any smoother.
